title: 1000+ Professional Photoshop Brushes -- CLEAN
description:
After painstaking downloading, compiling, and compressing, it's finally here.  More than 1000 professional grade Photoshop (7+) brushes contained within 60 brush packs, all in one RAR file for your convenience.

######################################################################################

INSTRUCTIONS FOR USING PHOTOSHOP BRUSHES

Windows: Place the *.abr files into:
Program Files>Adobe>Adobe Photoshop X>Presets>Brushes (where X is the version number for your version of Photoshop.)

Mac: Place the *.abr files into:
Applications>Adobe Photoshop>Presets>Brushes 

Restart photoshop and your brushes have been successfully loaded.

######################################################################################

ALWAYS CHECK TO MAKE SURE THE TORRENT YOU ARE DOWNLOADING IS CLEAN, EVEN IF THE UPLOADER IS A VIP/TRUSTED... Go to http://www.virustotal.com and upload the file to scan it.  Another tip is to see if it's possible to unpack the files you've downloaded if they're not RARs, etc.  If it is, it's probably because someone packed a virus into the file and then uploaded it to look like an innocent file.

HAPPY DOWNLOADING!
